  "details": "The libblockdev packages provide a C library with GObject introspection\nsupport used for low-level operations on block devices. The library serves\nas a thin wrapper around plug-ins for specific functionality, such as LVM,\nBtrfs, LUKS, or MD RAID.\n\nBug Fix(es) and Enhancement(s):\n\n* libblockdev doesn't run external utilities with LC_ALL=C and fails to\nparse their localized output (BZ#1895286)",
